            "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>git-ai status vs stats</title>\n<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body {\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\n    background: #0d1117;\n    color: #e6edf3;\n    padding: 40px 20px;\n    min-height: 100vh;\n  }\n  h1 {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #8b949e;\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n    margin-bottom: 48px;\n  }\n  .diagram {\n    max-width: 860px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* ── Timeline row ── */\n  .timeline {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: stretch;\n    gap: 0;\n    position: relative;\n    margin-bottom: 0;\n  }\n\n  /* Each stage box */\n  .stage {\n    flex: 1;\n    background: #161b22;\n    border: 1px solid #30363d;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 20px 16px 16px;\n    position: relative;\n    transition: border-color 0.2s;\n  }\n  .stage:hover { border-color: #58a6ff; }\n\n  /* Arrow connector between stages */\n  .arrow-wrap {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 0 4px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    width: 56px;\n  }\n  .arrow {\n    width: 100%;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 4px;\n  }\n  .arrow-line {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 2px;\n    background: #30363d;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .arrow-line::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    right: -1px;\n    top: -4px;\n    border: 5px solid transparent;\n    border-left-color: #30363d;\n  }\n  .arrow-cmd {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    color: #8b949e;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    background: #0d1117;\n    padding: 1px 5px;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    border: 1px solid #30363d;\n    font-family: \"SF Mono\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n  }\n\n  /* Stage header */\n  .stage-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n  .stage-title {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #e6edf3;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n  .stage-sub {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    color: #8b949e;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n\n  /* Storage badge */\n  .storage {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    font-family: \"SF Mono\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n    background: #1c2128;\n    border: 1px solid #30363d;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    padding: 6px 8px;\n    color: #79c0ff;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .storage-label {\n    color: #8b949e;\n    font-size: 9px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n    margin-bottom: 3px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── Command cards ── */\n  .commands-row {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 24px;\n    margin-top: 40px;\n  }\n  .cmd-card {\n    flex: 1;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    border: 1px solid;\n  }\n  .cmd-card.status {\n    background: #0f2b1f;\n    border-color: #2ea043;\n  }\n  .cmd-card.stats {\n    background: #111b2b;\n    border-color: #1f6feb;\n  }\n\n  .cmd-header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .cmd-badge {\n    font-family: \"SF Mono\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    padding: 4px 10px;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n  }\n  .status .cmd-badge { background: #2ea043; color: #fff; }\n  .stats  .cmd-badge { background: #1f6feb; color: #fff; }\n\n  .cmd-title { font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e; }\n\n  .cmd-body { font-size: 12px; color: #c9d1d9; line-height: 1.7; }\n  .cmd-body strong { color: #e6edf3; }\n\n  .tag {\n    display: inline-block;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    padding: 1px 7px;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-left: 6px;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n  }\n  .tag-green { background: #0f3d1f; color: #3fb950; border: 1px solid #2ea043; }\n  .tag-blue  { background: #0c2544; color: #58a6ff; border: 1px solid #1f6feb; }\n\n  /* Bracket / coverage arc */\n  .coverage-section { margin-top: 28px; }\n  .coverage-label {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    color: #8b949e;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n  .coverage-bar {\n    display: flex;\n    height: 28px;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    border: 1px solid #30363d;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n  }\n  .cov-seg {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);\n    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n    transition: opacity 0.2s;\n  }\n  .cov-seg:hover { opacity: 0.85; }\n  .cov-working  { background: #1a3a28; flex: 2; border-right: 1px solid #30363d; }\n  .cov-staging  { background: #1a2a3a; flex: 1; border-right: 1px solid #30363d; }\n  .cov-committed{ background: #1a2030; flex: 3; }\n\n  .cov-legend {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 16px;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    color: #8b949e;\n  }\n  .cov-dot {\n    display: inline-block;\n    width: 8px; height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    margin-right: 4px;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n  }\n\n  /* Pointer lines SVG overlay — done via pure CSS bracket approach */\n  .bracket-row {\n    margin-top: 32px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n\n  /* Simple visual bracket made with borders */\n  .bracket-status, .bracket-stats {\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 8px 12px;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-family: \"SF Mono\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .bracket-status {\n    background: #0f2b1f;\n    border: 1px dashed #2ea043;\n    color: #3fb950;\n  }\n  .bracket-stats {\n    background: #111b2b;\n    border: 1px dashed #1f6feb;\n    color: #58a6ff;\n  }\n  .bracket-desc {\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #8b949e;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    margin-left: 8px;\n    font-family: inherit;\n  }\n\n  .divider {\n    height: 1px;\n    background: #21262d;\n    margin: 36px 0;\n  }\n\n  /* example output block */\n  .example-block {\n    background: #161b22;\n    border: 1px solid #30363d;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 14px 16px;\n    font-family: \"SF Mono\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    color: #c9d1d9;\n    line-height: 1.8;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n  .ex-prompt { color: #8b949e; }\n  .ex-cmd    { color: #3fb950; }\n  .ex-cmd2   { color: #58a6ff; }\n  .ex-out    { color: #e6edf3; }\n  .ex-comment{ color: #484f58; }\n\n  footer {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 48px;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    color: #484f58;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"diagram\">\n\n  <h1>git-ai 归因数据流 · status vs stats</h1>\n\n  <!-- ── Stage row ── -->\n  <div class=\"timeline\">\n\n    <!-- Stage 1: AI edits working dir -->\n    <div class=\"stage\">\n      <div class=\"stage-icon\">✏️</div>\n      <div class=\"stage-title\">Working Directory</div>\n      <div class=\"stage-sub\">AI / 人工 在此修改文件<br>改动尚未进入 git 追踪</div>\n      <div class=\"storage\">\n        <div class=\"storage-label\">归因数据存储于</div>\n        .git/git-ai/working-log/<br>&lt;HEAD_SHA&gt;/\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"tag tag-green\">✓ status 可读</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"arrow-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"arrow\">\n        <div class=\"arrow-line\"></div>\n        <div class=\"arrow-cmd\">git add</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Stage 2: Staging Area -->\n    <div class=\"stage\">\n      <div class=\"stage-icon\">📋</div>\n      <div class=\"stage-title\">Staging Area (Index)</div>\n      <div class=\"stage-sub\">文件已 stage<br>等待提交</div>\n      <div class=\"storage\">\n        <div class=\"storage-label\">归因数据存储于</div>\n        .git/git-ai/working-log/<br>&lt;HEAD_SHA&gt;/\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"tag tag-green\">✓ status 可读</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"arrow-wrap\">\n      <div class=\"arrow\">\n        <div class=\"arrow-line\"></div>\n        <div class=\"arrow-cmd\">git commit</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Stage 3: Committed -->\n    <div class=\"stage\">\n      <div class=\"stage-icon\">📦</div>\n      <div class=\"stage-title\">Committed</div>\n      <div class=\"stage-sub\">提交完成，post-commit<br>hook 自动写入 git notes</div>\n      <div class=\"storage\">\n        <div class=\"storage-label\">归因数据存储于</div>\n        refs/notes/ai<br>(git object)\n      </div>\n      <span class=\"tag tag-blue\">✓ stats 可读</span>\n    </div>\n\n  </div><!-- /timeline -->\n\n\n  <!-- ── Coverage bar ── -->\n  <div class=\"coverage-section\" style=\"margin-top: 32px;\">\n    <div class=\"coverage-label\">命令覆盖范围</div>\n\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">\n      <div class=\"bracket-status\">\n        git-ai status\n        <span class=\"bracket-desc\">↔ 读取 working-log，覆盖\"最近一次 commit 之后\"的所有变更（含未 stage、已 stage）</span>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; margin: 4px 0 4px 12px;\">\n        <div style=\"flex:2; height:4px; background:#2ea043; border-radius:2px;\"></div>\n        <div style=\"flex:1; height:4px; background:#2ea043; border-radius:2px; opacity:0.6;\"></div>\n        <div style=\"flex:3; height:4px; background:#30363d; border-radius:2px;\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"bracket-stats\">\n        git-ai stats [commit-sha]\n        <span class=\"bracket-desc\">↔ 读取 git notes，默认分析 HEAD commit；支持区间 main..feature</span>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; margin: 4px 0 4px 12px;\">\n        <div style=\"flex:2; height:4px; background:#30363d; border-radius:2px;\"></div>\n        <div style=\"flex:1; height:4px; background:#30363d; border-radius:2px;\"></div>\n        <div style=\"flex:3; height:4px; background:#1f6feb; border-radius:2px;\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n  <!-- ── Command cards ── -->\n  <div class=\"commands-row\">\n\n    <div class=\"cmd-card status\">\n      <div class=\"cmd-header\">\n        <span class=\"cmd-badge\">git-ai status</span>\n        <span class=\"cmd-title\">查看当前未提交的 AI 贡献</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"cmd-body\">\n        <strong>何时用：</strong>写完代码还没 commit，想看 AI 写了多少行<br><br>\n        <strong>数据来源：</strong><br>\n        &nbsp;• working-log checkpoint 文件<br>\n        &nbsp;• 与 HEAD 做 <code>git diff</code> 计算行数<br><br>\n        <strong>注意：</strong>commit 之后 working-log 会清空，<br>\n        &nbsp;此时 status 将显示 \"No checkpoints\"\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example-block\">\n        <span class=\"ex-prompt\">$ </span><span class=\"ex-cmd\">git-ai status</span><br>\n        <span class=\"ex-out\">AI: 143 lines (+89%)  Human: 18 lines</span><br>\n        <br>\n        <span class=\"ex-out\">3 mins ago   +80   -0   Claude claude-3-7-sonnet</span><br>\n        <span class=\"ex-out\" style=\"color:#484f58\">12 mins ago  +18   -5   lyraile</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cmd-card stats\">\n      <div class=\"cmd-header\">\n        <span class=\"cmd-badge\">git-ai stats</span>\n        <span class=\"cmd-title\">查看已提交 commit 的 AI 贡献</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"cmd-body\">\n        <strong>何时用：</strong>commit 之后，或查历史某个提交的 AI 占比<br><br>\n        <strong>数据来源：</strong><br>\n        &nbsp;• <code>refs/notes/ai</code>（post-commit hook 写入）<br>\n        &nbsp;• 与 commit diff 做交集验证<br><br>\n        <strong>前提：</strong>必须已安装 hooks（<code>git-ai install-hooks</code>），<br>\n        &nbsp;否则 notes 不存在，stats 无数据\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"example-block\">\n        <span class=\"ex-prompt\">$ </span><span class=\"ex-cmd2\">git-ai stats</span><br>\n        <span class=\"ex-out\">AI: 89 lines (+73%)  Human: 33 lines</span><br>\n        <br>\n        <span class=\"ex-comment\"># 指定 commit</span><br>\n        <span class=\"ex-prompt\">$ </span><span class=\"ex-cmd2\">git-ai stats abc1234</span><br>\n        <br>\n        <span class=\"ex-comment\"># 查看 notes 原始内容</span><br>\n        <span class=\"ex-prompt\">$ </span><span class=\"ex-cmd2\">git notes --ref=ai show HEAD</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ── Troubleshooting hint ── -->\n  <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#1c1108; border:1px solid #9e6a03; border-radius:8px; padding:16px 20px; font-size:12px; color:#d29922; line-height:1.8;\">\n    <strong style=\"color:#e3b341;\">⚡ 常见疑问：同一批改动，status 能识别 AI，stats 却不行？</strong><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#8b949e;\">\n      1. 检查 hooks 是否安装：<code style=\"color:#d29922;\">ls .git/hooks/post-commit</code><br>\n      2. 检查 notes 是否写入：<code style=\"color:#d29922;\">git notes --ref=ai show HEAD</code><br>\n      3. 若无输出，重新安装：<code style=\"color:#d29922;\">git-ai install-hooks</code>，然后重新 commit\n    </span>\n  </div>\n\n</div><!-- /diagram -->\n\n<footer>git-ai · status reads working-log · stats reads git notes (refs/notes/ai)</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
